Restaurant Application

AngularJs application developed in the Cousera Course: Front End Javascript Frameworks: AngularJS

Description

The files provided here were used for completing the course programming assignments. It has code to use both grunt and gulp. Gulp may be a better build.

Setup:
Compile the folder 'Konkani' using gulp. Copy the files from the dist folder to json-server >> public. 
db.json contains data needed for the application. Feel free to change the data in this file.
In your command prompt, go to the json-server folder and type : "json-server --watch db.json". 
This should start up a server at port number 3000 on your machine. 
Now type:   http://localhost:3000/ in your browser to access the application.

